WEBVTT

01:48.010 --> 01:57.510
Modi must have told you very clearly about
how to grow in Sahaja Yog because he’s one

01:57.510 --> 02:06.220
of them who has really taken very positive
step to see that he grows.

02:06.220 --> 02:13.260
Now one has to understand one simple point
about realisation is that, just mere awakening

02:13.260 --> 02:19.580
of the Kundalini is not sufficient, that’s
just the beginning.

02:19.580 --> 02:28.769
You get your realisation but you must become
the tree, you have to grow, you have to become.

02:28.769 --> 02:37.230
If you cannot grow then you have not achieved
what you wanted to be.

02:37.230 --> 02:49.280
And you grow very fast, very fast with meditation
and with understanding about meditation.

02:49.280 --> 02:58.030
Now one of the few hurdles that we have, that
I’ve seen it, that are innately built in

02:58.030 --> 03:00.630
Sahaja Yog itself.

03:00.630 --> 03:06.020
One of them is that you get it spontaneously
so easily that you take it for granted.

03:06.020 --> 03:08.850
This is in the pattern of it, only innately
built.

03:08.850 --> 03:15.210
You see what ever you get so easily you just
take it for granted.

03:15.210 --> 03:21.320
But the another side of it is like that, that
when you have your eyes you don’t know the

03:21.320 --> 03:23.900
value of your eyes, you take it for granted.

03:23.900 --> 03:28.140
But when you don’t have them then you know
the value of eyes, it’s like that.

03:28.140 --> 03:35.410
So when you lose vibrations and when you get
out of Sahaja Yog, then you start feeling

03:35.410 --> 03:43.679
much more lost and then you come back to Sahaja
Yoga again.

03:43.679 --> 03:50.699
Like a person becomes rich, he enjoys the
riches and then you make him poor then he

03:50.699 --> 03:53.080
feels it more.

03:53.080 --> 03:54.550
So this is the correcting point.

03:54.550 --> 04:03.190
But it is very true that Sahaja has this thing
innately built in its self that it all happens

04:03.190 --> 04:10.559
very spontaneously and you get it for doing
nothing at all.

04:10.559 --> 04:21.919
So, may be so many of you may lose it because
you might find that it is just you got it

04:21.919 --> 04:22.919
because of something.

04:22.919 --> 04:28.350
I’ve also known of people they get vibrations
and they say, “Now it’s all right I don’t

04:28.350 --> 04:30.150
need Sahaja Yoga, I am on my own."

04:30.150 --> 04:36.309
Again they’re back like bad pennies with
some troubles and some problems and then they

04:36.309 --> 04:37.309
go out.

04:37.309 --> 04:44.141
Now I would say that Modi is one of those
first twelve people who got realisation, after

04:44.141 --> 04:49.339
two years I’ve worked on them, while you
got realisation in such a short time.

04:49.339 --> 04:56.680
Two years I’ve worked on twenty five people
out of which twelve got realisation you can

04:56.680 --> 05:01.900
imagine, two years! As I’ve told you in
London I’ve worked on six people for four

05:01.900 --> 05:06.979
years to give them realisation.

05:06.979 --> 05:14.750
But once a certain number of people of particular
ideologies of permutations and combinations,

05:14.750 --> 05:21.669
once they get realisation I find the rate
of realisation increases very fast.

05:21.669 --> 05:27.450
Like formally we never use to have anybody
in the program who has been to any other Guru,

05:27.450 --> 05:28.940
just avoid them.

05:28.940 --> 05:35.390
Even up to the point that this Modi himself
used to tell people there’s no program today,

05:35.390 --> 05:36.690
no program.

05:36.690 --> 05:40.100
And they would ring Me up and find out that
there was a program and why they were not

05:40.100 --> 05:41.100
allowed.

05:41.100 --> 05:42.540
They said “Mother we get headaches you see.

05:42.540 --> 05:47.140
They break our necks and they just disturb
us and they are good for nothing."

05:47.140 --> 05:53.040
But now, it’s very different, once we have
built up our strength of collectivity we have

05:53.040 --> 05:57.370
so many channels, things are working out very
differently.

05:57.370 --> 06:04.840
So the value that Modi would attach to his
realisation is much more than you would attach

06:04.840 --> 06:06.560
normally.

06:06.560 --> 06:16.590
Because as you see, first even say to have
a ordinary oil lamp was a problem.

06:16.590 --> 06:19.740
So the oil lamp was very important for people.

06:19.740 --> 06:24.660
They would see to it that they would not use
out all the oil and they were so careful.

06:24.660 --> 06:28.880
But today we have no problem, we have got
electricity we take it for granted.

06:28.880 --> 06:33.670
Only when the electricity goes off we know
what is electricity is.

06:33.670 --> 06:43.400
In the same way your realisation also, when
it is lost you understand the value of it.

06:43.400 --> 06:49.930
But supposing you have just touched it and
then you lose it, then you do not understand.

06:49.930 --> 06:55.470
But if you’ve got it you’ve enjoyed it
then you lose it then you want it back again,

06:55.470 --> 07:01.490
so best thing is to be steadily moving towards
your evolution.

07:01.490 --> 07:08.060
Now after I go away that’s the fears people
have here that people start doubting.

07:08.060 --> 07:11.330
They said, “It happened with people they
started doubting."

07:11.330 --> 07:13.300
Doubting what?

07:13.300 --> 07:17.890
Your doubting yourself is the main point is.

07:17.890 --> 07:21.680
You cannot believe that you can get realisation.

07:21.680 --> 07:24.420
This is the basic.

07:24.420 --> 07:33.450
You see to Me, it seems that you feel that
how can you get realisation?

07:33.450 --> 07:40.450
Only those who are very highly realised souls
know that you are realised, they know that

07:40.450 --> 07:44.840
you have been given realisation, but they
also sometimes ask Me, “Why did you give

07:44.840 --> 07:45.840
them realisation.

07:45.840 --> 07:53.120
What have they done?” Because you also think,
I mean we still have to look forward to something

07:53.120 --> 07:54.440
else.

07:54.440 --> 07:56.550
How can we get realisation, this is the trouble

07:56.550 --> 07:59.540
You don’t believe in yourself.

07:59.540 --> 08:04.580
That’s what you have to have confidence
in yourself and then you’ll have confidence

08:04.580 --> 08:07.270
in Me also.

08:07.270 --> 08:12.170
Because there are so many ways, by which you
can verify.

08:12.170 --> 08:13.210
First of all

08:13.210 --> 08:24.680
you can ask questions to the photograph or
to Me in your heart, about Myself, My relationship

08:24.680 --> 08:31.020
what ever you think could be, what ever you
think, put your imagination and see that what

08:31.020 --> 08:32.950
you think I could have been.

08:32.950 --> 08:34.470
Ask that question.

08:34.470 --> 08:37.510
Your vibrations will answer.

08:37.510 --> 08:44.190
Put your, stretch your imagination to the
last, what could be the last word you could

08:44.190 --> 08:45.750
think of Me.

08:45.750 --> 08:52.030
You see, some people will put doubts saying
that, “Kundalini awakening is very difficult,

08:52.030 --> 08:54.090
it is not easy."

08:54.090 --> 09:00.030
Yes it’s true, it’s not easy, it’s a
very difficult things for human beings.

09:00.030 --> 09:03.280
You just can’t do it, is a fact.

09:03.280 --> 09:12.340
You have to work for days with some guru in
some jungle all alone, seeing nobody, working

09:12.340 --> 09:16.170
out your chakras by chakras, sometimes you
have to starve, sometimes you have to eat,

09:16.170 --> 09:19.910
sometimes you have to breathe, you have to
do all kinds of things.

09:19.910 --> 09:21.300
And then the guru can work out.

09:21.300 --> 09:31.990
But there could be someone who is somehow
the master, could be someone.

09:31.990 --> 09:38.450
Kundalini is the Holy Ghost within you.

09:38.450 --> 09:46.210
So there could be someone like that who can
do the job and that is what it is.

09:46.210 --> 09:53.760
These things put you into doubts, because
you can’t believe it.

09:53.760 --> 09:56.450
In relation to yourself you can’t believe
it.

09:56.450 --> 10:00.630
You can believe in God, you can believe in
Holy Ghost, you can believe in Christ but

10:00.630 --> 10:07.510
you cannot believe that it has any relationship
with you, that you could be that great, that

10:07.510 --> 10:10.440
you could get your realisation.

10:10.440 --> 10:12.350
So just feel it and enjoy it.

10:12.350 --> 10:14.640
First of all, don’t think, that’s why
I say, “Don’t think."

10:14.640 --> 10:17.081
Because as soon as you start thinking, Mr.

10:17.081 --> 10:23.369
Thomas in you will get up and say that “Hello,
this cannot be Self-realisation."

10:23.369 --> 10:24.369
Mr.

10:24.369 --> 10:26.390
Thomas was great, you see.

10:26.390 --> 10:33.040
Christ had all the disciples and I find all
those types around, permutations and combinations

10:33.040 --> 10:37.030
and some how Judas also, but they’re rarely
to be found.

10:37.030 --> 10:45.450
But there are, no doubt and some are Thomas’s,
and these Thomas’ are described as murmuring

10:45.450 --> 10:47.100
souls by Christ Himself.

10:47.100 --> 10:51.850
He said, “These are murmuring souls,”
and they murmur and one murmuring soul comes

10:51.850 --> 10:57.090
to you, another murmuring soul in you joins
hands and you start all murmuring together,

10:57.090 --> 10:58.090
start thinking.

10:58.090 --> 11:02.770
Now at that time what have you to do on rational
grounds is very simple.

11:02.770 --> 11:05.350
What have I done so far?

11:05.350 --> 11:12.180
I’ve done everything, did I get cool breeze?

11:12.180 --> 11:16.040
Did I get my self realisation?

11:16.040 --> 11:20.420
Did I feel my own powers?

11:20.420 --> 11:23.420
Have I been able to feel myself and others?

11:23.420 --> 11:30.110
Because you see your still not fully realised,
you may not be able to feel the vibrations

11:30.110 --> 11:34.890
of another person, neither you will be able
to feel your own vibrations.

11:34.890 --> 11:41.730
But there are so many people here who are
realised and they can feel yours, and they

11:41.730 --> 11:42.810
can verify.

11:42.810 --> 11:49.140
Supposing they ask you, “How is your father?”

11:49.140 --> 11:52.510
There was one gentleman in England he came
and told Me, “Why is everybody asking me

11:52.510 --> 11:53.510
about my father?”

11:53.510 --> 11:57.960
I said, “Because there’s one particular
centre that’s catching,” and I called

11:57.960 --> 12:02.240
a child I said now tell Me, “What is the
centre catching?” She pointed out this one

12:02.240 --> 12:04.110
and I said, “This is the centre."

12:04.110 --> 12:07.280
Everybody is catching on this centre, this
is the father centre so they’re asking you

12:07.280 --> 12:08.390
about your father.

12:08.390 --> 12:12.540
He said, “Yes he’s dead and he died of
cancer and he had this and that,” and we

12:12.540 --> 12:13.980
had to treat him.

12:13.980 --> 12:20.140
For example anorexia is a disease can be cured
by curing this centre.

12:20.140 --> 12:28.110
It’s such a deep knowledge and it is such
an all pervading knowledge.

12:28.110 --> 12:36.520
Because once you know in a tree the sap that
goes to all the leaves and all the ends of

12:36.520 --> 12:41.571
it and if you can move the sap, your attention
can move with the sap, you can know the whole

12:41.571 --> 12:44.060
of the tree.

12:44.060 --> 12:49.160
You cannot know leaves and then know the tree.

12:49.160 --> 12:51.200
How many leaves can you count?

12:51.200 --> 12:56.340
But to know the tree the best thing is to
get to the sap.

12:56.340 --> 13:00.760
To treat a tree is best is to get to its sap,
isn’t it?

13:00.760 --> 13:11.040
In the same way when you go from inside out
then you find that you know yourself and others

13:11.040 --> 13:12.040
very well.

13:12.040 --> 13:15.950
It’s very simple even small children can
do it.

13:15.950 --> 13:22.210
So the first doubt comes about yourself, “Oh
this is one of them” because there’s a

13:22.210 --> 13:23.700
guru shopping going on, you see.

13:23.700 --> 13:30.979
There’s a guru shopping, there’s a float,
you go to one guru to another, to ESPs and

13:30.979 --> 13:38.360
what you call them, all sorts of things, mediums,
and all sorts of things they do with the dead

13:38.360 --> 13:39.950
bodies or anything.

13:39.950 --> 13:43.910
All these things you have been to and you
will have found it.

13:43.910 --> 13:49.930
So now suddenly you have to come to a temple,
where you don’t pay anything and you just

13:49.930 --> 13:50.930
get the blessings.

13:50.930 --> 13:56.630
So can’t believe it, you just can’t believe
it, it’s too much to believe.

13:56.630 --> 13:58.330
This is what happens you get

13:58.330 --> 13:59.330
confused.

13:59.330 --> 14:05.430
You are all ready confused, but confusion
could be over by understanding that something

14:05.430 --> 14:10.100
is happening to you just wait and see, give
it a chance.

14:10.100 --> 14:17.970
There’s no way we can bind you to Sahaja
Yoga, because there’s no mesmerism here.

14:17.970 --> 14:21.560
This is another innately a problem with Sahaja
Yoga.

14:21.560 --> 14:27.700
Second problem I should say is that you’re
too free to do what you like, absolutely free,

14:27.700 --> 14:35.900
there’s no binding force except that you
feel the love of your Mother.

14:35.900 --> 14:39.900
Supposing you are not feeling the vibrations
in your hand, there’s no way of binding

14:39.900 --> 14:42.050
you down to Sahaja Yog, nothing.

14:42.050 --> 14:47.170
We just advise “Go ahead, it will work out,
let it work out."

14:47.170 --> 14:52.020
There is no fees, there’s no registration,
there’s no compulsion, nothing.

14:52.020 --> 14:54.410
It’s your own free will.

14:54.410 --> 14:59.950
If you want to stick on you can stick on,
if you want to go away you can go away.

14:59.950 --> 15:03.090
There’s no force on you of any kind.

15:03.090 --> 15:08.750
There’s no registration of your names with
some fees or anything, I mean you are not

15:08.750 --> 15:11.450
bound to pay anything.

15:11.450 --> 15:14.421
If you paid something then you feel, “All
right I’ve paid for it, so go through it

15:14.421 --> 15:16.010
what ever it is, good or bad..

15:16.010 --> 15:20.170
Supposing you go to see a play and it’s
a horrid play but still you say, “All right

15:20.170 --> 15:22.780
I’ve paid for it so let me go through it."

15:22.780 --> 15:28.500
But that you cannot do with Sahaja Yog because
you’ve not paid.

15:28.500 --> 15:33.130
There’s nobody will force you down, nobody
will go on telephoning to you, “Come along,

15:33.130 --> 15:34.840
please come along,” and all that.

15:34.840 --> 15:38.239
So the attitude has to be changed, it is I
who has to gain.

15:38.239 --> 15:42.130
Say there’s a beautiful spot somewhere.

15:42.130 --> 15:47.489
Now that beautiful spot doesn’t send an
invitation card to anyone, everybody goes

15:47.489 --> 15:48.489
there.

15:48.489 --> 15:52.400
But if you have not yet discovered the beauty
of Sahaja Yog in that way and have not enjoyed

15:52.400 --> 15:55.751
it fully, you’ll have to go again and again
and see for yourself.

15:55.751 --> 16:03.880
It is a deliberation on your side not on the
side of the Sahaja Yogis or Sahaja Yoga.

16:03.880 --> 16:06.710
It’s not going to fall at your feet.

16:06.710 --> 16:12.620
That please come to Sahaja Yoga, please donate
something, nothing of the kind.

16:12.620 --> 16:19.180
If you come you are welcome, if you don’t
come, welcome.

16:19.180 --> 16:24.710
On the contrary, you will be surprised there’s
more rejection than acceptance in Sahaja Yog.

16:24.710 --> 16:26.270
That’s also innately built.

16:26.270 --> 16:30.231
I’ve seen some people who are very insincere
type they just go out from Sahaja Yoga like

16:30.231 --> 16:31.860
a tangent.

16:31.860 --> 16:37.510
There was a gentleman who was very troublesome
to us in Bombay and we didn’t know what

16:37.510 --> 16:46.380
to do with him and he just got transferred
from there and we got rid of him.

16:46.380 --> 16:54.860
So you just go out of Sahaja Yoga like a tangent
and we are saved from the botheration.

16:54.860 --> 16:59.870
Because you must understand, if you have problems,
if you are not all right it’s a problem

16:59.870 --> 17:01.730
for Sahaja Yogis to correct you.

17:01.730 --> 17:08.120
It’s just the other way round, if you understand
this, then you will understand the thing,

17:08.120 --> 17:09.120
what works out.

17:09.120 --> 17:13.910
For example if I have to cure somebody it’s
a problem for Me and not the problem for the

17:13.910 --> 17:16.120
person who’s sick.

17:16.120 --> 17:23.500
Now if the tree has to grow is the problem
for the gardener not for the tree.

17:23.500 --> 17:32.320
So the tree must see to it that it co-operates
with the gardener and gets itself developed.

17:32.320 --> 17:38.380
If this understanding is developed, that it
is I who has to gain, it is I who has to go

17:38.380 --> 17:46.400
forward, Mother has not to gain from me anything,
She wants me to have all my powers manifested.

17:46.400 --> 17:53.950
She wants me to grow through it, if this attitude
is developed then you’ll work hard to grow

17:53.950 --> 17:56.190
and you’ll work it out.

17:56.190 --> 18:01.920
But on the contrary you see at the slightest
protest if you ego stands up and says, “Why,

18:01.920 --> 18:06.190
why should I do this?”

18:06.190 --> 18:12.020
To overcome this hurdle you see, we have to
build up certain stages.

18:12.020 --> 18:16.180
That’s what Modi was telling Me.

18:16.180 --> 18:20.320
That you first become thoughtlessly aware,
see that silence is established.

18:20.320 --> 18:27.230
There are certain things that you do much
later, everybody is not allowed in there,

18:27.230 --> 18:34.680
because truth can be only born by people who
are strong enough to bear it.

18:34.680 --> 18:44.110
That’s why I’m not going to tell you who
am I, till you reach a certain stage, because

18:44.110 --> 18:45.680
you cannot bear the light.

18:45.680 --> 18:48.310
That’s what happened with Christ.

18:48.310 --> 18:52.650
They crucified Him because they could not
bear Him.

18:52.650 --> 18:59.529
Human beings are like that, they can’t even
bear an incarnation of love.

18:59.529 --> 19:03.470
They can’t even bear love, it’s too much
for them.

19:03.470 --> 19:09.400
Even if you give them too much love they get
upset, they get disturbed, they just can’t

19:09.400 --> 19:10.400
bear it.

19:10.400 --> 19:14.991
So you have to build up yourself to come to
a certain stage of understanding of Sahaja

19:14.991 --> 19:15.991
Yoga.

19:15.991 --> 19:17.660
It’s a state, which you achieve.

19:17.660 --> 19:19.620
It’s a state.

19:19.620 --> 19:25.870
You are not to be certified by anyone on the...But
it’s a state where you will start giving

19:25.870 --> 19:32.389
realisation to others and the whole way you’ll
be talking you will be in a very different

19:32.389 --> 19:34.830
manner as if you are completely detached.

19:34.830 --> 19:38.490
You’ll say “It is going, it is coming."

19:38.490 --> 19:39.490
It happens.

19:39.490 --> 19:44.460
You will not say my mother must get, my father
must get, you will never say like that.

19:44.460 --> 19:51.840
Because you’ll understand that the problem
of Sahaja Yoga is that it cannot give to anyone.

19:51.840 --> 19:53.050
Like

19:53.050 --> 20:00.560
the sunshine can shine it is for the trees
to expose themselves to the sunshine and get

20:00.560 --> 20:03.060
the advantage of it.

20:03.060 --> 20:09.450
The sunshine is not going to run after you
all over to see that you get it.

20:09.450 --> 20:18.240
This is the point here, it will shine the
whole day and you take it.

20:18.240 --> 20:23.100
But it’s not that it will run after you
all the time requesting you, “Oh please

20:23.100 --> 20:28.200
get me, oh please get me, have it, have it,”
like that.

20:28.200 --> 20:37.680
And this is what one has to understand very
clearly, that it is you who has to ask for

20:37.680 --> 20:42.600
it, and not anybody is going to force on you
anything.

20:42.600 --> 20:49.570
On the contrary if anybody tries to say something
more your ego gets like that.

20:49.570 --> 20:52.040
So try to be careful.

20:52.040 --> 20:58.180
I am very happy to know that also, that in
all the ego orientated societies I’ve seen

20:58.180 --> 21:00.680
that Sahaja Yoga works like wonders.

21:00.680 --> 21:03.850
Because first thing they see is their colossal
ego.

21:03.850 --> 21:08.350
And that’s a very positive point about it,
because once you start seeing this horrible

21:08.350 --> 21:14.960
balloon in you, you just start watching yourself
and enjoying, “Oh Mr so and now get along

21:14.960 --> 21:15.960
with your ego."

21:15.960 --> 21:18.820
You see it’s a very interesting life you
start leading.

21:18.820 --> 21:25.200
If your ego you see, is a very good sign.

21:25.200 --> 21:28.460
If you cannot see your ego then there’s
danger.

21:28.460 --> 21:32.019
But some can even see their super ego if they’re
possessed.

21:32.019 --> 21:38.240
See people see how they get possessed suddenly
because the frequency of possession becomes

21:38.240 --> 21:46.570
very little so that there’s a big gaps you
see to see the time when you are normal and

21:46.570 --> 21:51.610
when you get abnormal also you can see clearly
that you are abnormal.

21:51.610 --> 21:58.230
By seeing that you start judging, “Oh God
I have again been caught up, I’m again lost,”

21:58.230 --> 22:00.120
and you come back to normal.

22:00.120 --> 22:09.610
The whole thing becomes a very beautiful understanding
of the reality about yourself and you laugh

22:09.610 --> 22:11.730
at yourself all the time.

22:11.730 --> 22:16.460
All the time you laugh at your self and you
laugh at everything and you find the whole

22:16.460 --> 22:21.860
joke going round how people are seriously
indulging into nonsensical things and how

22:21.860 --> 22:28.270
it’s such a big joke you’ve been yourself
worrying about things which have no meaning,

22:28.270 --> 22:30.360
which has no significance.

22:30.360 --> 22:35.810
Like I went first to Paris and people told
Me, “Mother they are not going to like you

22:35.810 --> 22:41.720
very much, because they believe a person who
is so happy is ignorant.

22:41.720 --> 22:43.160
You should not be a happy person.

22:43.160 --> 22:46.509
You should be a crying baby so they’ll believe
You."

22:46.509 --> 22:51.530
They’re all les miserable, very unhappy
people, extremely unhappy and if you tell

22:51.530 --> 22:56.230
them you are a happy person so they are going
to be shocked at such a thing.

22:56.230 --> 23:00.360
I said, “Really this Les Miserable, let
me (inaudible).

23:00.360 --> 23:06.050
Let Me do something about them and I made
them laugh so much at their miseries that

23:06.050 --> 23:10.389
they got all right and they understood that
the joy is just there.

23:10.389 --> 23:15.880
You have to just peep in your heart and you’ll
find the source of your joy and then the whole

23:15.880 --> 23:17.540
thing vanishes into thin air.

23:17.540 --> 23:21.030
But it has to work, it has to happen.

23:21.030 --> 23:29.100
There is no quick way of doing it in the sense
that I say, “All right you give me five

23:29.100 --> 23:32.690
rupees or five dollars, Australian dollars
and you get it."

23:32.690 --> 23:37.120
NO, no, no, no, you may give Me any amount
it won’t work out.

23:37.120 --> 23:40.580
It has not worked out with My own daughters
you’ll be surprised.

23:40.580 --> 23:43.180
I’ve never forced them or I’ve never asked
them.

23:43.180 --> 23:46.580
I’ve only two daughters they’re not realised
I’m not bothered.

23:46.580 --> 23:49.440
When they’ll ask for it they’ll get it.

23:49.440 --> 23:51.600
But My four grandchildren are born realised.

23:51.600 --> 23:57.300
And one of the eldest ones one day very seriously
said, “As it is you cannot commit mistakes

23:57.300 --> 24:05.040
I know but it would have been nice if you
have given them realisation when they were

24:05.040 --> 24:06.040
children."

24:06.040 --> 24:12.090
You see this is what it is that you cannot
force these things on anyone and you have

24:12.090 --> 24:14.930
to take a very detached view.

24:14.930 --> 24:20.350
You are a seeker, your mother and you are
there but they are not your responsibility,

24:20.350 --> 24:22.160
you can tell them about Sahaja Yog.

24:22.160 --> 24:26.139
But if they are opposing you better have,
let them be alone, they’ll come round.

24:26.139 --> 24:31.210
When they see the transformation in within
you, they’ll definitely come.

24:31.210 --> 24:32.940
So leave them alone.

24:32.940 --> 24:35.080
Don’t bother your heads.

24:35.080 --> 24:41.400
Just leave them alone and you will be amazed
that they will see you transforming so well

24:41.400 --> 24:47.600
and acting so well and they’ll change themselves
and they will come to you and ask you, “How

24:47.600 --> 24:55.030
are you so much changed and transformed?”
You see proof of the pudding is in seeing

24:55.030 --> 24:59.990
the pudding up there changing people.

24:59.990 --> 25:06.950
And this transformation you’ll be amazed
coming into you so suddenly that you will

25:06.950 --> 25:09.520
be amazed.

25:09.520 --> 25:16.650
But as I told you that on the left side is
the desire or you can say the super ego, the

25:16.650 --> 25:18.310
desire to do something.

25:18.310 --> 25:26.600
And the right side is the ego which we try
to sort of please and which feels happy and

25:26.600 --> 25:28.330
the one by which we have ambitions.

25:28.330 --> 25:32.519
But in the centre is the will power to do
this.

25:32.519 --> 25:38.310
And this will power has to be increased by
you, “I have to do it, I have to do it."

25:38.310 --> 25:39.710
First you’ll feel tired because

25:39.710 --> 25:43.400
your left heart is weak, then I will tell
you how to do it.

25:43.400 --> 25:46.820
‘Then know how to raise your left heart
if you’re tired.

25:46.820 --> 25:52.620
See most of the people these days are very
tired people.

25:52.620 --> 25:54.840
They talk, “Ah,” they sit down “Ah."

25:54.840 --> 25:59.150
They can’t, I mean they are very tired,
absolutely fagged out people.

25:59.150 --> 26:01.850
Morning till evening what have you been doing,
nothing.

26:01.850 --> 26:07.850
Just sitting in the sun you got tired, just
lazing out you got tired.

26:07.850 --> 26:10.000
Why, why did you get tired?

26:10.000 --> 26:15.060
Firstly because you’re not integrated you
are fighting with in yourself.

26:15.060 --> 26:20.060
You’re head is fighting your heart, your
heart is fighting your liver.

26:20.060 --> 26:24.220
Secondly, you are thinking and wasting your
energy.

26:24.220 --> 26:32.850
So you have to learn how to settle your heart,
what has to be done to raise your heart to

26:32.850 --> 26:38.330
make it peaceful and how to get the energy
from your spirit.

26:38.330 --> 26:42.770
Once you start doing that your tired feeling
will go away.

26:42.770 --> 26:48.850
Then your aggressiveness also will decrease
and you’ll be amazed that you will just

26:48.850 --> 26:50.129
watch the whole thing.

26:50.129 --> 26:56.800
Neither you’ll aggress nor you’ll take
aggression and the whole reaction will be

26:56.800 --> 26:58.220
very different.

26:58.220 --> 27:03.330
Then everything has a meaning, your feelings
have a meaning.

27:03.330 --> 27:08.990
Supposing you have a feeling today for Poland,
which is in trouble, all of you should ask

27:08.990 --> 27:11.910
just now, “Mother solve the problem of Poland."

27:11.910 --> 27:17.200
Because I have no desires you see, I am desire
less, you have to ask and it works, you’ll

27:17.200 --> 27:21.790
be amazed because your attention is enlightened
now, it just works.

27:21.790 --> 27:24.220
You have to desire for it and it works.

27:24.220 --> 27:25.220
You have to work for it and it works.

27:25.220 --> 27:32.050
And so many miraculous things people will
tell you just believe them that’s all true.

27:32.050 --> 27:39.610
Money problem solved, because of Lakshmi Tattwa
within, financial problems solved, social

27:39.610 --> 27:45.060
problem solved, family problems solved because
you are solved.

27:45.060 --> 27:48.070
See in relation to you all everything seems
problematic.

27:48.070 --> 27:52.389
When your problems are solved everything is
solved.

27:52.389 --> 27:54.830
It’s so simple as that.

27:54.830 --> 27:59.990
We have to solve ourselves and it is solved
through the awakening of the Kundalini.

27:59.990 --> 28:05.110
Now I would like to have some questions from
you and then I would like you to go into groups

28:05.110 --> 28:12.139
with the Sahaja Yogis and talk to them on
intimate level and also you must tell Me your

28:12.139 --> 28:13.139
problems.

28:13.139 --> 28:15.889
If you have any intimate problems, you can
talk to Me also.

28:15.889 --> 28:22.820
But best is to talk to each other.
I would like Warren to see to it that he organises

28:22.820 --> 28:24.759
all these groups properly.

28:24.759 --> 28:38.430
But I would love to have some questions from
you about Sahaja Yoga now.

28:38.430 --> 28:43.520
Question: How can one laugh at abortion.

28:43.520 --> 28:49.970
He's talking about abortion, you are taking
the view that it is bad?

28:49.970 --> 28:57.450
Shri Mataji: I’m not saying you have to,
I said you are not to laugh, means you laugh

28:57.450 --> 29:00.740
at silly stupid things I meant, you see.

29:00.740 --> 29:06.210
But at abortion as I can’t understand you
see.

29:06.210 --> 29:08.550
This is a very funny situation in this country.

29:08.550 --> 29:11.730
As it is the birth rate is minus and you are
having abortions.

29:11.730 --> 29:15.330
Question: Does it exist in India much abortion

29:15.330 --> 29:18.720
Shri Mataji: Not much, people don’t like
it at all, they hate it.

29:18.720 --> 29:21.860
And you know the trouble is like this.

29:21.860 --> 29:25.860
You people are having no children so we have
to have the load on us.

29:25.860 --> 29:28.110
You see what to do?

29:28.110 --> 29:32.470
Nobody to be born here, they don’t want
to be born here because there is no love in

29:32.470 --> 29:34.160
the heart.

29:34.160 --> 29:38.269
See when the other day when somebody told
Me about the doctors here some of them are

29:38.269 --> 29:40.920
butchers I couldn’t believe it.

29:40.920 --> 29:44.190
Because in India at least, doctors are not
butchers by any chance.

29:44.190 --> 29:48.940
I was surprised; this is because everything
has become a butchery here, because the heart

29:48.940 --> 29:50.970
is covered with ego.

29:50.970 --> 29:53.540
There’s no heart left.

29:53.540 --> 29:55.160
You have to raise the heart.

29:55.160 --> 30:01.340
That’s important, once you raise the heart,
you see you cannot stand all this nonsense,

30:01.340 --> 30:02.340
you know.

30:02.340 --> 30:04.370
Why do you want to have abortion I still can’t
understand?

30:04.370 --> 30:07.110
Question: Does it affect Swadisthan charka?

30:07.110 --> 30:11.420
Shri Mataji: Oh, it affects many chakras,
I mean.

30:11.420 --> 30:18.090
There was someone I knew who always used to
catch on right heart, I must tell you this,

30:18.090 --> 30:20.340
very nice person, always on right heart.

30:20.340 --> 30:27.610
His father was a good man everything was fine,
asked him, “How are you catching on right

30:27.610 --> 30:33.370
heart?” He was not married and when he came
very close to Me then he confessed to Me that,

30:33.370 --> 30:40.820
“I lived with a woman and she was going
to have a baby and she went in for an abortion

30:40.820 --> 30:45.120
and I conceded, and since then

30:45.120 --> 30:49.879
I have been feeling very sad about the whole
thing."

30:49.879 --> 30:56.889
But the whole view about life has to be changed
then only you can avoid these things.

30:56.889 --> 30:59.519
You see it is a symptom of a disease.

30:59.519 --> 31:05.629
It’s not the disease itself, abortion is
not the disease, is a symptom of a disease.

31:05.629 --> 31:12.770
Now what is the disease with in us is, is
that, that we have allowed our sex to be let

31:12.770 --> 31:16.330
loose completely, talking too much about sex
from childhood.

31:16.330 --> 31:19.920
What is the need to give education in sex,
I’ve been failed to understand?

31:19.920 --> 31:25.570
Openly, there’s no need to teach about,
you see, do the animals need any sex education,

31:25.570 --> 31:27.690
they still produce.

31:27.690 --> 31:35.530
Then they told Me, “They tell about sex
only because they think by telling about sex

31:35.530 --> 31:38.389
they can protect people from not going into
sex."

31:38.389 --> 31:42.320
I said, “No, they create too much of curiosity
in children."

31:42.320 --> 31:47.830
For example, in India we never talk about
sex to children, they do not know, they are

31:47.830 --> 31:48.830
so innocent.

31:48.830 --> 31:54.460
Even till the marriage takes place some of
the girls do not know what sex actually is,

31:54.460 --> 31:55.990
how it works out and all.

31:55.990 --> 32:01.580
But they are told this is something filthy
to do and all that and when the girl gets

32:01.580 --> 32:07.420
into puberty it is told and to the boys also,
somehow or other it is a very different society.

32:07.420 --> 32:11.150
This question doesn’t come, it never comes
into the head of the boys and girls.

32:11.150 --> 32:16.900
You see if you keep them pure, like it doesn’t
come in the head of a sister and a brother

32:16.900 --> 32:20.139
even today, thank God.

32:20.139 --> 32:24.650
Many sisters and brothers I should say despite
Freud’s all efforts to spoil your minds,

32:24.650 --> 32:27.110
but still there are brothers and sisters relations
today.

32:27.110 --> 32:33.690
In the same way it doesn’t come into their
heads at all.

32:33.690 --> 32:38.620
And when they get married they are to be told,
this is what it is.

32:38.620 --> 32:43.310
And that’s why they say these koarak and
all these places were built where they could

32:43.310 --> 32:47.860
take young brides and young people to see
that.

32:47.860 --> 32:54.300
This was called as Koomari Kar Temple, means
the married women when they were not virgins

32:54.300 --> 33:01.230
could go there and see those places to understand
what is sex is and they got so exhausted with

33:01.230 --> 33:05.660
this early sex life, I mean you go into all
kinds of tantrums then.

33:05.660 --> 33:08.750
Because you’re so exhausted then you go
into perversions.

33:08.750 --> 33:10.369
The basics are wrong.

33:10.369 --> 33:13.980
We are trying too hard to be sexologists.

33:13.980 --> 33:19.570
There’s no need to be sex points you are
that already.

33:19.570 --> 33:24.889
But you don’t want to be only sex points,
do you?

33:24.889 --> 33:35.531
I don’t know what makes you feel that that
is the end of every, every endeavor, everything

33:35.531 --> 33:36.710
should end up there.

33:36.710 --> 33:41.769
May be that advertisement and all this is
coming to you too much because they think

33:41.769 --> 33:44.360
that by exploiting these things they will
help you.

33:44.360 --> 33:58.790
But it’s such a perverted thing and

33:58.790 --> 34:13.810
Seeker interrupts and asks Shri Mataji about
people in India being given a gift like a

34:13.810 --> 34:15.570
transistor radio for sterilization.

34:15.570 --> 34:18.870
Does it have a purpose?

34:18.870 --> 34:28.040
It has a purpose to a point.....Oh I'm sorry
this has another point....

34:28.040 --> 34:32.820
He is talking about in India where they give
a transistor radio....

34:32.820 --> 34:40.509
Shri Mataji: That’s what they try, this
is also, you see western ideas coming to India.

34:40.509 --> 34:43.930
Oh, they did all sorts just to sterilise them.

34:43.930 --> 34:48.320
Oh! that’s how the lady lost her last election,
last election she has now pulled her ears

34:48.320 --> 34:49.320
for that.

34:49.320 --> 34:53.850
You see, they are all westernised people you
see, they try to try all these tricks in....

34:53.850 --> 34:55.550
People don’t like it you see.

34:55.550 --> 35:08.660
There’s a bridegroom who went for his wedding
and poor thing saw that there was a team of

35:08.660 --> 35:10.379
people standing there for sterilisation.

35:10.379 --> 35:18.480
He jumped out of the bus and he disappeared
forever, nobody knows where he is, disappeared.

35:18.480 --> 35:24.840
‘And they even sterilised people who were
very old and who were not even married you

35:24.840 --> 35:25.840
see.

35:25.840 --> 35:30.250
It’s so funny, so indiscriminate, I think
they were possessed by some bhoots I don’t

35:30.250 --> 35:31.610
know what to call them.

35:31.610 --> 35:40.020
You see population is a problem in India but
what to do now, you should solve the problem.

35:40.020 --> 35:43.860
And there is something working out in a very
funny way, I must tell you.

35:43.860 --> 35:49.160
I went to Colombia, I found lots of these
Norwegians carrying Colombian children with

35:49.160 --> 35:50.160
them.

35:50.160 --> 35:54.619
And they looked so different from Norwegian
children, Norwegian people and these Colombian

35:54.619 --> 35:55.619
children.

35:55.619 --> 35:58.879
I asked them, “Why do you acquire these
children where are you carrying them?

35:58.879 --> 36:04.099
They said “We have adopted them”.
I said, “Why don’t you produce your own?

36:04.099 --> 36:05.920
That would be better, to produce your own."

36:05.920 --> 36:12.750
"No we don’t want to go through the process
of it, it’s better to have ready made."

36:12.750 --> 36:19.170
So the supply has started in having all this
in developing countries to give you ready

36:19.170 --> 36:20.170
made children.

36:20.170 --> 36:25.499
Isn’t if funny, it’s funny things going
on, instant babies.

36:25.499 --> 36:36.079
Question: If a chakra is blocked and you clean
the chakras wouldn’t you being undoing the

36:36.079 --> 36:42.309
karmic cycle that a person has to go through?

36:42.309 --> 36:48.421
Shri Mataji: Very good idea, Because I think
you people...I know the question is this,

36:48.421 --> 36:53.939
that he is saying that if you try to clean
the chakras you will be undoing the karmic

36:53.939 --> 37:00.969
cycle and all that you see this is the typical
things that are being circulated in the west

37:00.969 --> 37:01.989
you see.

37:01.989 --> 37:07.100
That you have your own karmas you see and
we are the gurus so you have to go through

37:07.100 --> 37:11.140
your karmas, you must suffer for your karmas
you see like that is there.

37:11.140 --> 37:17.630
Now, this theory was all right before Christ
came in, not after His coming.

37:17.630 --> 37:19.959
And why are they here then?

37:19.959 --> 37:22.679
Why are we paying them, for what?

37:22.679 --> 37:24.509
You better pickle them out.

37:24.509 --> 37:29.410
They’re worth nothing because they just
take money from you, and we have to go through

37:29.410 --> 37:30.410
our karmas.

37:30.410 --> 37:33.410
They make you dance, jump go into all kinds
of things.

37:33.410 --> 37:36.489
Put spirits in us and say, “You are suffering
your karmas.

37:36.489 --> 37:42.850
Why should we suffer?” At least they should
suffer for our karma’s minimum of minimum.

37:42.850 --> 37:44.979
Now Christ has done that for you.

37:44.979 --> 37:49.380
He has taken all these karmas, your karmas
upon Himself.

37:49.380 --> 37:55.459
He has made way for us, that’s why you have
to pass through Him.

37:55.459 --> 38:03.100
Once you pass through Him, through Agnya chakra,
your karmas are sucked in by Him, that’s

38:03.100 --> 38:04.499
your ego.

38:04.499 --> 38:09.309
It’s the only ego that says you have done
this wrong, and that wrong.

38:09.309 --> 38:14.039
You see an animal doesn’t think that way.

38:14.039 --> 38:17.719
It thinks it’s it own sva bhavah the way
it has to be.

38:17.719 --> 38:22.340
But it’s only the human beings who think
I’ve done this wrong, I’ve done that wrong.

38:22.340 --> 38:25.460
I’ve done this good, that bad because we
have ego.

38:25.460 --> 38:35.400
But when your Kundalini passes through your
Agnya chakra your ego is sucked in, your superego

38:35.400 --> 38:36.400
is sucked in.

38:36.400 --> 38:41.059
Christ has done double job in one shot you
know, it’s great.

38:41.059 --> 38:48.380
That’s why He was crucified, it was to be.

38:48.380 --> 38:56.120
He took all your karmas upon Himself and put
it into hell.

38:56.120 --> 39:03.179
So what ever karmas you have done are all
sucked in.

39:03.179 --> 39:05.420
But the door must open fully.

39:05.420 --> 39:10.739
In the beginning it happens that only a thread
comes up, you see, and the ego is not fully

39:10.739 --> 39:14.850
sucked in so sometimes it still comes up and
all that.

39:14.850 --> 39:19.690
The best weapon to get rid of them is to forgive
others.

39:19.690 --> 39:26.509
Forgiveness is the greatest weapon Christ
has given us, which we have to use, forgive,

39:26.509 --> 39:28.430
forgive and forgive.

39:28.430 --> 39:37.529
That’s a very good way, Lords Prayer is
the solution for your Agnya charka, you’ll

39:37.529 --> 39:38.610
be amazed.

39:38.610 --> 39:44.170
You have to say Lords Prayer after realisation
to open your Agnya.

39:44.170 --> 39:46.380
Then you become thoughtlessly aware.

39:46.380 --> 39:50.840
After realisation again I say, not before
realisation, it has no meaning.

39:50.840 --> 39:54.829
Before realisation what ever you have said
has gone into karmas.

39:54.829 --> 40:02.079
Only after realisation you are baptized and
get an opening here and all your karmas pass

40:02.079 --> 40:05.499
through that.

40:05.499 --> 40:09.679
Also you will find when you get realisation
lot of heat comes out these are the karmas

40:09.679 --> 40:13.100
you see, that are coming out.

40:13.100 --> 40:16.940
Let the heat go out and all karmas are finished.

40:16.940 --> 40:18.640
It’s like that.

40:18.640 --> 40:21.739
This is what is Self-Realisation.

40:21.739 --> 40:31.400
Like an egg is in a egg shell is very different,
but when it becomes a little chick and the

40:31.400 --> 40:41.449
mother breaks the tip of the egg a new bird
comes out with out any karmas or the smell

40:41.449 --> 40:43.699
of the egg.

40:43.699 --> 40:48.920
So clean and nice, every thing converted into
something beautiful.

40:48.920 --> 40:55.140
It’s like that, this is the rebirth.

40:55.140 --> 41:00.160
This is how we become a new personality a
new being.

41:00.160 --> 41:03.203
So to forget about your karmas after your
realisation, all right.

41:03.203 --> 41:06.059
He has said it

41:06.059 --> 41:11.699
that, “He died for your sins."

41:11.699 --> 41:14.650
Didn’t He?

41:14.650 --> 41:17.779
And the wages of sin is fear.

41:17.779 --> 41:22.630
If you still have fear within you of your
karmas, you are still sinning.

41:22.630 --> 41:26.559
There should be no fear about it.

41:26.559 --> 41:32.249
Do not have any guilt, I’ve been telling
you not to have any guilt.

41:32.249 --> 41:35.220
What can you do?

41:35.220 --> 41:36.220
What sins can you commit?

41:36.220 --> 41:40.150
Do not have any fears.

41:40.150 --> 41:45.590
This is very common as I told you the other
day left Vishuddhi, I have to talk about it

41:45.590 --> 41:46.590
quite a lot.

41:46.590 --> 41:51.920
It’s so common, in Australia, in America
and in all the western countries, to feel

41:51.920 --> 41:52.920
guilty.

41:52.920 --> 41:57.410
Everything collapses there and nobody can
rise through the Agnya because it collapses

41:57.410 --> 42:00.630
down here onto left Vishuddhi where you feel
guilty.

42:00.630 --> 42:02.650
What are you feeling guilty about?

42:02.650 --> 42:04.640
And why did Christ come on this earth.

42:04.640 --> 42:07.170
You are just wasting His incarnation by feeling
guilty yourself.

42:07.170 --> 42:11.809
He has taken all your guilt upon Himself.

42:11.809 --> 42:15.079
What do you thing He was?

42:15.079 --> 42:22.799
He was Omkara, he was Pranava, He was the
word, He was that power.

42:22.799 --> 42:33.020
He’s not attached to anything but He can
take away everything that you think is sin,

42:33.020 --> 42:38.009
because He’s sinless, He so pure, immaculate.

42:38.009 --> 42:41.749
All right does that give you some hopes?

42:41.749 --> 42:46.400
Or still you are indulging into your own miseries?

42:46.400 --> 42:50.729
Question: Can You give us some guide about
diet.

42:50.729 --> 42:52.179
Shri Mataji: Diet?

42:52.179 --> 42:53.179
All right.

42:53.179 --> 42:57.559
This diet theory is also coming from some
horrible Brahmins you see.

42:57.559 --> 42:59.749
Don’t listen to them.

42:59.749 --> 43:04.219
They are the greatest rakshasas ever born
on this earth.

43:04.219 --> 43:07.069
Devils, rakshasas are monsters.

43:07.069 --> 43:12.601
They eat like hell, they eat such a lot and
they always tell you, “Don’t do this and

43:12.601 --> 43:16.999
don’t do that."

43:16.999 --> 43:23.650
You can eat anything you like except don’t
eat the meat of animals which are bigger than

43:23.650 --> 43:24.650
you.

43:24.650 --> 43:31.660
I mean other wise you will develop muscles
which will have funny contours and things.

43:31.660 --> 43:38.249
Eat animals which are smaller than you is
the point is.

43:38.249 --> 43:46.799
And if you eat those animals they do not also
have much sense of compassion and all that.

43:46.799 --> 43:51.380
It’s all right they are just like vegetables
sort of things, so it doesn’t matter.

43:51.380 --> 43:55.480
You don’t kill them, they are killed in
the machine and all that, you have to eat

43:55.480 --> 43:57.880
that, and you need it, you have to eat.

43:57.880 --> 44:01.840
But that doesn’t mean that if you are vegetarians
you should become non vegetarians.

44:01.840 --> 44:03.039
It doesn’t mean that.

44:03.039 --> 44:04.579
What ever you eat, you can eat.

44:04.579 --> 44:08.600
Eating is not going to change your spirit.

44:08.600 --> 44:21.259
Spirit doesn’t eat, it does not, makes no
difference to the spirit except that, to your

44:21.259 --> 44:25.049
body which is the lamp.

44:25.049 --> 44:29.169
So if you have to keep the wick all right,
you have to keep the lamp all right and for

44:29.169 --> 44:34.309
that don’t eat anything that is a very big
animal compared to yourself.

44:34.309 --> 44:38.620
Cows meat for example in India they don’t
eat, because, “Have you ever seen Indian

44:38.620 --> 44:40.900
cows they’re very gentle."

44:40.900 --> 44:46.259
And the cows are in the house, just like mother
they start giving milk to the children they

44:46.259 --> 44:47.259
see.

44:47.259 --> 44:51.140
Every day they are taking the milk of the
cows so they develop a feeling, you see.

44:51.140 --> 44:52.929
And that’s why they don’t drink, you see.

44:52.929 --> 44:57.610
But it doesn’t mean that if your Australian
cows are I don’t think are like that.

44:57.610 --> 45:04.489
Because what I’ve seen they look like buffalos
to Me sometimes.

45:04.489 --> 45:10.350
Like My granddaughter, she came to England
and she asked Me, “Mother, Grandmother,

45:10.350 --> 45:15.170
why the buffalos in England are white?”
Yes, so, it’s all right.

45:15.170 --> 45:17.650
But you’ll come down on diet.

45:17.650 --> 45:20.110
It will be different you see, you’ll see
gradually.

45:20.110 --> 45:21.789
But don’t worry about it.

45:21.789 --> 45:25.410
Gradually everything drops out into very little
things.

45:25.410 --> 45:27.280
But you allow yourself to develop.

45:27.280 --> 45:28.280
Question: Eggs?

45:28.280 --> 45:29.280
And things like that?

45:29.280 --> 45:31.400
Shri Mataji: Oh, eggs you better have, lots
of it.

45:31.400 --> 45:33.840
But if you have liver it’s not good to have
eggs.

45:33.840 --> 45:38.700
Eggs is very heating,, pork is otherwise good
but not good for the people who have liver

45:38.700 --> 45:39.700
problem.

45:39.700 --> 45:42.079
See you must understand that every person
is different.

45:42.079 --> 45:44.870
Now today I met a lady who is very left sided.

45:44.870 --> 45:47.229
So I had to tell her, “You eat pork, eggs
everything.

45:47.229 --> 45:49.739
You see it is how you are.

45:49.739 --> 45:51.329
Even the Indian Ayurveda is like that.

45:51.329 --> 45:56.569
They want to know the prakruti, the character
of a person how he is.

45:56.569 --> 45:59.669
We have evolved from different types of animals.

45:59.669 --> 46:01.410
I saw the nocturnal ones.

46:01.410 --> 46:06.850
You see the nocturnal ones must eat a lot
of meats, those who have evolved from nocturnal

46:06.850 --> 46:07.850
side, you see.

46:07.850 --> 46:13.499
Left-sided, the ones who are afraid and frightened
and who are not egoistical at all you see.

46:13.499 --> 46:18.660
Such types they should take more meats and
things but those who are too much aggressive

46:18.660 --> 46:21.009
better take to vegetables, is better.

46:21.009 --> 46:26.840
All right now, what’s the question?

46:26.840 --> 46:36.960
Question: Does forgiveness stop the rich getting
richer and the poor getting poorer?

46:36.960 --> 46:38.969
Shri Mataji: It does absolutely, absolutely.

46:38.969 --> 46:43.690
Sahaja Yoga is the thing that balances the
society.

46:43.690 --> 46:51.179
Those who are poor become richer and the rich
understand that they must share.

46:51.179 --> 46:57.100
Willingly they start sharing their money.

46:57.100 --> 47:01.150
But you become really rich in a very miraculous
manner.

47:01.150 --> 47:05.759
Now there’s a girl here and I would like
her to tell you what happened to her, it’s

47:05.759 --> 47:06.759
miraculous.

47:06.759 --> 47:10.039
But she’s an Australian and she doesn’t
tell lies you can see that very clearly and

47:10.039 --> 47:13.539
she’ll tell you what happened to her.

47:13.539 --> 47:18.989
Where is she gone?

47:18.989 --> 47:22.640
Sharon come along..is she here?

47:22.640 --> 47:31.410
No let her tell, is better, she’s Australian
they’ll believe her more.

47:31.410 --> 47:37.259
But never trust an Indian that’s even worse.

47:37.259 --> 47:44.269
You know some of the gurus have introduced
some Indian bhoots, Indian spirits into English

47:44.269 --> 47:50.370
people, and Americans and also European and
I find they behave just like Indians.

47:50.370 --> 47:54.470
They’ll cheat, they embezzle, they’ll
take away things, not the women, they’ll

47:54.470 --> 47:56.299
not touch the women you see.

47:56.299 --> 48:02.719
But they’ll touch the things they take away
the empty cans, is typical Indian you see.

48:02.719 --> 48:04.209
It’s rather

48:04.209 --> 48:09.779
surprising, yes there are some, I’ve seen
them like that.

48:09.779 --> 48:15.329
It’s surprising to see such things happening
to a western person who behaves just like

48:15.329 --> 48:21.499
an Indian must be some possession of bhoots
put by these gurus.

48:21.499 --> 48:28.539
So if you believe Me then I can tell you what
she’s told, it’s really miraculous, very

48:28.539 --> 48:30.299
miraculous, you see.

48:30.299 --> 48:36.400
Cheryl was telling Me that she wanted to come
to India and she had no money.

48:36.400 --> 48:46.999
So her daughter was very anxious to come to
India and they didn’t know what to do, they

48:46.999 --> 48:47.999
didn’t have sufficient money.

48:47.999 --> 48:55.999
So they just said, “Mother we want to come
to India can you arrange it for us, that’s

48:55.999 --> 48:56.999
all."

48:56.999 --> 49:01.140
And it so happened that this girl had taken
a trinket she had in the house, a bracelet

49:01.140 --> 49:04.880
to the school for a sale, whenever they have
the fetes all over.

49:04.880 --> 49:09.509
So she took that for the fete and the teacher
said, “I think this is gold."

49:09.509 --> 49:12.269
She couldn’t believe it.

49:12.269 --> 49:17.019
She brought it home and they got it valued
and they found that the price of the thing

49:17.019 --> 49:21.419
was equal to what they had to spend for both
of them travels.

49:21.419 --> 49:23.269
But this is nothing.

49:23.269 --> 49:26.779
And then she got some money from somewhere
in the house, somewhere I don’t know how

49:26.779 --> 49:29.749
she got some money and she didn’t sell even
the bracelet.

49:29.749 --> 49:31.910
And that’s still there she said, “For
the next trip."

49:31.910 --> 49:34.670
I said, “I hope so, you sell it."

49:34.670 --> 49:35.670
“May not."

49:35.670 --> 49:42.660
Like that you see, things work out, because
your Laxshmi Tattawa, your centre of well

49:42.660 --> 49:45.640
being gets enlightened and then you are looked
after.

49:45.640 --> 49:47.360
So many things happen.

49:47.360 --> 49:54.239
Like today they told Me so many things of
this kind happening to them and I too.

49:54.239 --> 49:59.709
You see when these people came in, I had told
them all right, you give Me so much money

49:59.709 --> 50:02.110
may be required for your stay there.

50:02.110 --> 50:07.499
Very little it was, very little for them to
be there in India after all, you see India

50:07.499 --> 50:10.319
is also now becoming very expensive.

50:10.319 --> 50:14.219
And when I went to India I had discovered
it had become very expensive, doesn’t matter

50:14.219 --> 50:15.499
I said, “I’ll put it in the bank.

50:15.499 --> 50:16.919
“Let it be there."

50:16.919 --> 50:23.120
And anybody ask Me, “Have it, you want it,
have it, now spend go,” and it was all right.

50:23.120 --> 50:28.669
I could manage, see that’s what he did,
and so many of them have done it.

50:28.669 --> 50:29.969
It’s looked after.

50:29.969 --> 50:35.920
You go to right places, you get right things,
don’t spend too much, you do not repent

50:35.920 --> 50:41.729
for spending and you feel happy for whatever
you have.

50:41.729 --> 50:46.549
You feel very joyous, not worried about counting
but if you make a budget you had it.

50:46.549 --> 50:53.400
You don’t worry your head about budgeting,
how much your going to spend, you’ll be

50:53.400 --> 50:54.400
surprised.

50:54.400 --> 50:56.380
You won’t go to things which are unnecessary,
useless but you’ll buy something that is

50:56.380 --> 51:03.620
very good and ultimately these things will
be very precious for you to sell.

51:03.620 --> 51:06.729
Many things have happened like that.

51:06.729 --> 51:10.979
Many things have happened.

51:10.979 --> 51:15.140
Question: Why is Australia important for the
future?

51:15.140 --> 51:17.370
Maybe about Shri Ganesha?

51:17.370 --> 51:22.669
Shri Mataji: Only thing I don’t want to
pamper the ego.

51:22.669 --> 51:26.610
Question: Is Australia blessed?

51:26.610 --> 51:29.870
Shri Mataji: Very much, very much blessed.

51:29.870 --> 51:39.019
It’s a very much blessed place, specially
created.

51:39.019 --> 51:48.519
Australia was the first continent to be created
and if I dare to answer this question, I hope

51:48.519 --> 51:54.059
you’ll believe Me and not get into ego trips.

51:54.059 --> 52:08.519
Australia is a place which is described in
the ancient Puranas that a great saint was

52:08.519 --> 52:16.340
sent to Australia and another heaven was created.

52:16.340 --> 52:26.239
And that saint is called as Thrishanku which
is your Southern Cross...what do you call

52:26.239 --> 52:28.169
that?

52:28.169 --> 52:32.329
That shows the Southern Cross and you can
only see Southern Cross from Australia.

52:32.329 --> 52:43.360
This is one of the Puranas, the Vedas have
also mentioned this and even before that Australia

52:43.360 --> 52:45.279
is the place which has the Ganesha.

52:45.279 --> 52:53.660
The first is the Mooladhara Chakra, the first
centre is in Australia.

52:53.660 --> 52:57.759
How much wise you should be.

52:57.759 --> 53:03.620
Did you hear Me?

53:03.620 --> 53:12.219
Question: She wanted your opinion about the
Australian aboriginals.

53:12.219 --> 53:19.809
Shri Mataji: Oh, they must have been good
people to begin with, I am sure of it.

53:19.809 --> 53:28.710
They must have been very good and holy people
and nice people but I think later on they

53:28.710 --> 53:37.209
deviated because of too much jungles and things
you know, they started feeling the fear of

53:37.209 --> 53:38.569
the nature too much.

53:38.569 --> 53:46.590
They must have worshiped things, which were
good to begin with and later on to some things

53:46.590 --> 53:49.370
like spirits and this.

53:49.370 --> 53:55.610
More over the dead bodies the way they disposed
of must have been something wrong.

53:55.610 --> 54:04.890
So maybe they might have gone into a left
sided action into primitive ways of exciting

54:04.890 --> 54:05.890
these bhoots

54:05.890 --> 54:09.600
and things, spirits and spiritualism and all
that.

54:09.600 --> 54:13.920
But in Australia must be the minimum, in Africa
is horrible.

54:13.920 --> 54:19.699
African countries have too much of it but
it should be the minimum of minimum because

54:19.699 --> 54:25.489
you see, Ganesha’s chakra is connected with
the left side, you see is more on the left

54:25.489 --> 54:26.989
side isn’t it?

54:26.989 --> 54:34.799
So also one can go drift more on to the left
side that is what it is.

54:34.799 --> 54:41.279
And even today I feel there’s kind of a
lurking inferiority complex that works in

54:41.279 --> 54:42.279
Australians.

54:42.279 --> 54:46.799
They try to copy the west, there’s nothing
to copy there, they’ve nothing sensible.

54:46.799 --> 54:48.989
They have to learn from you.

54:48.989 --> 54:52.979
You see this is a little inferiority complex
we have that all the best things are in the

54:52.979 --> 54:53.979
west.

54:53.979 --> 54:58.509
That’s wrong, you are much better of in
so many ways.

54:58.509 --> 55:01.160
At least you’ve not lost your moorings.

55:01.160 --> 55:07.900
So I would not pass a general remark about
a community as such but there is a possibility

55:07.900 --> 55:09.660
that they can come up very well too.

55:09.660 --> 55:12.140
I mean they can get out of all that left-sidedness.

55:12.140 --> 55:20.370
In India also we have big communities in the
south where people have lived with too much

55:20.370 --> 55:26.979
ritualism and all that and have taken to left-sided
behaviour of attracting you know spirits and

55:26.979 --> 55:29.459
this and that, and giving those [telesmart?]
and all that.

55:29.459 --> 55:34.739
They have done all that they are doing, like
witchcraft, witch doctors and all that.

55:34.739 --> 55:39.650
They must be doing it, but it can be cured
there’s no problem.

55:39.650 --> 55:45.430
As the west, people are over developed and
very ego orientated and right side.

55:45.430 --> 55:48.909
Both are extreme cases, but you can be correct.

55:48.909 --> 55:54.569
The people who are left side it’s easier
because they have to move forward but it’s

55:54.569 --> 55:57.150
difficult for ego orientated to move backwards.

55:57.150 --> 56:01.019
But if we can do that there why not here,
so nothing is lost.

56:01.019 --> 56:04.900
One should not worry too much about these
things.

56:04.900 --> 56:09.319
Human begins are just the same everybody has
Kundalini, finished.

56:09.319 --> 56:19.419
As long as you have Kundalini I have no problem.

56:19.419 --> 56:23.759
Question: Is there anything wrong with eating
chilies?

56:23.759 --> 56:27.519
Shri Mataji: No, it suits some people very
much.

56:27.519 --> 56:32.130
Some people should have, those who suffer
from colds will be a good idea, suffer from

56:32.130 --> 56:34.019
constipation is a good idea.

56:34.019 --> 56:36.150
But don’t eat too much of anything.

56:36.150 --> 56:41.309
But it’s good for some people, something
is good for some people, something is good

56:41.309 --> 56:42.989
for some people, you have to just find out.

56:42.989 --> 56:47.439
For people who get constipated it is better
to have a little of green chilies all the

56:47.439 --> 56:50.490
time, it is very rich in vitamin C.

56:50.490 --> 57:01.340
It is very rich in vitamin C is good for people
who catch colds very easily.

57:01.340 --> 57:07.989
Question: Do you know anything about the teaching
called Mahikari

57:07.989 --> 57:10.929
Shri Mataji: I know.

57:10.929 --> 57:20.600
You see Mahikari thing was, the person who
started Mahikari was a realised soul, though

57:20.600 --> 57:22.420
not so well equipped.

57:22.420 --> 57:30.419
I’ve met him before his realisation and
he got realisation I think through Me only,

57:30.419 --> 57:31.469
what ever it was.

57:31.469 --> 57:34.329
I do not want to claim anything like that.

57:34.329 --> 57:36.410
But only thing is he was not equipped, well
equipped.

57:36.410 --> 57:39.539
Like anybody here who gets realisation starts
doing something.

57:39.539 --> 57:44.019
And his daughter I think, mislead the people
because she’s not a realised soul.

57:44.019 --> 57:49.239
She became very money-orientated, she started
putting it, it’s happened with every one

57:49.239 --> 57:50.239
of them.

57:50.239 --> 57:56.100
But poor thing, this one was not, he just
got realisation he was not an incarnation

57:56.100 --> 57:58.100
also, you see.

57:58.100 --> 58:06.789
Even incarnations who came on this earth like
Christ you see, like Mohammad Sahab, like

58:06.789 --> 58:12.149
Rama, Krishna see such great incarnations
were purest of pure.

58:12.149 --> 58:18.959
Even those people have been mishandled and
people have raised organisations, which are

58:18.959 --> 58:21.409
just money making propositions.

58:21.409 --> 58:23.069
Everything some how man makes into money.

58:23.069 --> 58:28.149
I don’t know how, it’s something that
happens to human beings you see.

58:28.149 --> 58:33.559
Then they start giving [Telesmart?] then they
start giving this, that, cross, this I mean

58:33.559 --> 58:35.739
it’s a money-making proposition through
out.

58:35.739 --> 58:39.769
You see this is the trouble.

58:39.769 --> 58:44.930
Warren: She said you are right.

58:44.930 --> 58:52.709
Shri Mataji: And you may lose lots of your
powers, even ordinary, normal powers with

58:52.709 --> 59:02.239
this kind of a wrong attitude you see, or
misguidance, because it happens like that,

59:02.239 --> 59:04.840
you can make mistakes, you can do so many
things.

59:04.840 --> 59:12.590
You know I’ve seen people, one girl whom
I had given realisation she went to a lady

59:12.590 --> 59:13.979
who was a medium.

59:13.979 --> 59:17.229
She used to get “Ho, ho, ho, ho,” like
that, and this thing.

59:17.229 --> 59:18.229
And she

59:18.229 --> 59:21.709
gave her a talisman and she became actually
blind, actually blind.

59:21.709 --> 59:27.900
Now she’s blind, her eyes are open, I mean
I have to still cure her.

59:27.900 --> 59:31.649
This is the report I got about her.

59:31.649 --> 59:35.968
Question: Would you say the same of the Hari
Krishna Organisation?

59:35.968 --> 59:37.799
Shri Mataji: Oh, now you are pulling Me into
controversy.

59:37.799 --> 59:42.049
But I will tell you the other way round.

59:42.049 --> 59:47.959
You see if you go on calling say the name
of anybody, even your name would you like

59:47.959 --> 59:48.959
it?

59:48.959 --> 59:51.329
So then how can God like it?

59:51.329 --> 59:59.249
On the Oxford Street you stand up, you should
see the site, they even sell those things

59:59.249 --> 01:00:03.979
see like wigs, they sell them like wigs in
the market.

01:00:03.979 --> 01:00:07.949
They shave off and sometimes they wear wigs.

01:00:07.949 --> 01:00:13.380
See it’s not show, it is something that
has to happen within.

01:00:13.380 --> 01:00:18.809
It’s not the show that you put up is something
that has to happen.

01:00:18.809 --> 01:00:25.689
You see most of them end up with throat cancer
and very violent, very violent people.

01:00:25.689 --> 01:00:30.120
They are beggars’ absolute parasites.

01:00:30.120 --> 01:00:33.539
Warren: with expensive cars.

01:00:33.539 --> 01:00:40.209
Shri Mataji: You see this is very nice,
I met somebody in England and I told him,

01:00:40.209 --> 01:00:42.679
“What do you do here?” He said, “I deal
in opium."

01:00:42.679 --> 01:00:46.990
I got a fright.
I said, “Opium, how do you deal in opium?”

01:00:46.990 --> 01:00:50.579
“Other people’s money,”
I said, “That’s very good, other people’s

01:00:50.579 --> 01:00:51.579
money."

01:00:51.579 --> 01:00:52.729
You see you can float an enterprise.

01:00:52.729 --> 01:00:59.799
It’s very easy because you are such seekers
such great seekers of ages and you are so

01:00:59.799 --> 01:01:01.489
naïve, very good.

01:01:01.489 --> 01:01:09.029
You go anywhere they’ll take a square, sit
there with saffron cloths with some circles

01:01:09.029 --> 01:01:11.149
on, another fellow will be fanning.

01:01:11.149 --> 01:01:15.929
Oh this one is very great, coming direct from
Kashi.

01:01:15.929 --> 01:01:18.019
Then have nothing to do with horrible people.

01:01:18.019 --> 01:01:22.819
Kashi is one of the worst places now.

01:01:22.819 --> 01:01:27.209
So you all go and prostrate.

01:01:27.209 --> 01:01:28.529
This is what it is.

01:01:28.529 --> 01:01:33.860
I mean, why are you enamoured by these circuses,
aren’t you fed up with them?

01:01:33.860 --> 01:01:39.860
We had a lady from Norway, this one was very
interesting.

01:01:39.860 --> 01:01:44.400
She came to My house stayed with Me, very
badly caught up, and she told Me the story

01:01:44.400 --> 01:01:45.999
of a lama who came to Norway.

01:01:45.999 --> 01:01:50.850
First he told all these Norwegians, “You
see, if I have to come to Norway you have

01:01:50.850 --> 01:01:54.669
to make a place with the floor which has got
all marble."

01:01:54.669 --> 01:01:55.829
Look at that.

01:01:55.829 --> 01:01:58.159
They’re such parasites these Lamas are.

01:01:58.159 --> 01:02:03.600
First they have sucked the blood of these
poor Tibetans and now they were willing to

01:02:03.600 --> 01:02:04.880
suck the blood of these Norwegians.

01:02:04.880 --> 01:02:09.850
Now these poor young people you see, I should
say the young people in the west are really

01:02:09.850 --> 01:02:14.919
not rich because they’re parents do not
give them money the way we give our children

01:02:14.919 --> 01:02:15.919
you see.

01:02:15.919 --> 01:02:21.890
So they starve themselves, they ate only potatoes
and this and that and for one year they starved

