and proves it.

01:23:02.340 --> 01:23:06.710
Question: What influence are you likely to
have on those around him or on people who

01:23:06.710 --> 01:23:09.750
live with You who are not realised.

01:23:09.750 --> 01:23:17.000
What is the realised souls influence in that
type of environment?

