like a medicine.

01:32:18.240 --> 01:32:20.720
Chanting is a mantra.

01:32:20.720 --> 01:32:32.760
Mantra means a thing that acts as a sound
to correct a particular thing within you,

01:32:32.760 --> 01:32:33.800
all right.

01:32:33.800 --> 01:32:37.430
It’s you can say sound therapy it is, all
right.

01:32:37.430 --> 01:32:43.470
Now you have to know what medicine is needed
for which charka, also you must know where

01:32:43.470 --> 01:32:47.920
is the problem with you, or with anybody else.

01:32:47.920 --> 01:32:53.590
I mean it would be chanting at random means
sometimes it would be sort of an indiscriminate

01:32:53.590 --> 01:32:56.360
drinking of all the medicines, you see.

01:32:56.360 --> 01:33:00.590
Taking all the medicines bottles into your
stomach emptying them without understanding.

01:33:00.590 --> 01:33:05.500
We do chant but we know where to chant, what.

01:33:05.500 --> 01:33:07.960
You see, not indiscriminate, just like that.

01:33:07.960 --> 01:33:13.560
And it’s very dangerous because when you
go on chanting say, Rama’s name or Krishna’s

01:33:13.560 --> 01:33:14.560
name.

01:33:14.560 --> 01:33:18.610
Now when you say Krishna’s name, Krishna
is here, if your Kundalini has not reached

01:33:18.610 --> 01:33:24.430
there up to this point if you take Krishna’s
name it’s very, very annoying for Krishna

01:33:24.430 --> 01:33:27.180
Himself and He recedes, sleeps off.

01:33:27.180 --> 01:33:33.470
He freezes sometimes and by that you develop
problems of the chakras and sometimes you

01:33:33.470 --> 01:33:37.840
