01:33:37.840 --> 01:33:44.020
So first, you must know where is your Kundalini,
where it has gone, where it has stopped.

01:33:44.020 --> 01:33:48.410
Then you should know what is the problem,
then you must know what exactly is the chanting

01:33:48.410 --> 01:33:51.560
to be used, all right, and then cure that
part.

01:33:51.560 --> 01:33:58.010
You see so it’s a big science, which has
to be understood in Sahaja Yoga, it’s not

01:33:58.010 --> 01:33:59.010
at random.

01:33:59.010 --> 01:34:04.780
You are suffering from whatever trouble you
are suffering from, you must know first of

01:34:04.780 --> 01:34:05.780
all.

01:34:05.780 --> 01:34:10.830
See many people who are Christians catch on
Agnya I told you, they do, because it’s

01:34:10.830 --> 01:34:11.830
unauthorised.

