01:39:39.690 --> 01:39:46.720
While Indians if they understand with their
wisdom they better short circuit this need

01:39:46.720 --> 01:39:49.860
not go into plastics and nylons.

01:39:49.860 --> 01:39:55.340
You see I have to carry nylon saris from England
for Indians while they have their silks they

01:39:55.340 --> 01:39:56.350
want to wear nylon.

01:39:56.350 --> 01:40:03.000
So this is the difference in the basic development.

01:40:03.000 --> 01:40:08.020
But Indians if they take to Sahaja Yoga they’re
very good and easy, especially Indian villagers

01:40:08.020 --> 01:40:09.020
are excellent.

01:40:09.020 --> 01:40:12.600
They don’t understand all this they have
no mental problems you see.

01:40:12.600 --> 01:40:16.640
I don’t have to discuss with them all these
things, they have not gone into all this nonsense

01:40:16.640 --> 01:40:20.600
so they suddenly become beautiful fruits,
that’s all.

01:40:20.600 --> 01:40:27.310
So this is the difference of little degrees
I would say that you are gone to other extreme

01:40:27.310 --> 01:40:33.320
and you still have to move to that extreme
or they may finish off and we can achieve

01:40:33.320 --> 01:40:34.320
results.

01:40:34.320 --> 01:40:38.670
But your quest is much ardent, very sincere
and truth.

01:40:38.670 --> 01:40:45.900
One more thing I always felt and today also
I feel that really some great souls are born

01:40:45.900 --> 01:40:53.110
in the west, that’s why is such a sincere
desire, very sincere in their desire.

01:40:53.110 --> 01:40:58.320
Indians first they come to Me for curing,
if not for curing for getting children if

01:40:58.320 --> 01:41:02.750
not for that for jobs or money all sorts of
thing they come up.

01:41:02.750 --> 01:41:07.350
Or they’ll say, “My mother is sick, my
father is sick, my brother is this,” all

01:41:07.350 --> 01:41:08.440
this goes on.

01:41:08.440 --> 01:41:14.010
But I have met many, many seekers in the west
who just want realisation, very beautiful

01:41:14.010 --> 01:41:15.910
people no doubt.

01:41:15.910 --> 01:41:21.720
But you have lost something in your seeking,
no doubt, doesn’t matter.

01:41:21.720 --> 01:41:42.100
Kundalini is that ardent desire within you,
which works it out.

01:41:42.100 --> 01:41:52.220
Question: It seems as though the simpler the
life we lead the better we are, it is much

01:41:52.220 --> 01:41:53.220
easier for us.

01:41:53.220 --> 01:41:54.430
We get away from thinking and so on.

01:41:54.430 --> 01:42:02.380
Shri Mataji: I agree is a good idea of simplicity
but is a, you must understand that also very

01:42:02.380 --> 01:42:06.950
clearly because we had somebody who was a
hippy I should say.

01:42:06.950 --> 01:42:13.570
He was a real hippy, such big grown, he had
grown hair up to this much and all that.

01:42:13.570 --> 01:42:18.320
He came to Me and scarcely wearing anything
in the horrible English cold you see.

01:42:18.320 --> 01:42:22.050
I said, “What are you doing to yourself
why don’t you clad your self properly into

01:42:22.050 --> 01:42:26.600
proper clothes and better cover yourself,”
and I was really didn’t understand him.

01:42:26.600 --> 01:42:30.740
I said, “You are not living in Africa why
are you dressed up like this, it’s like

01:42:30.740 --> 01:42:31.740
a primitive dress."

01:42:31.740 --> 01:42:33.410
He said, “I want to be primitive."

01:42:33.410 --> 01:42:35.960
I said, “You cannot by dressing up.

01:42:35.960 --> 01:42:41.360
Your brain is so over developed how can you
be primitive."

01:42:41.360 --> 01:42:43.590
You see by dressing up something do you become
that.

01:42:43.590 --> 01:42:49.160
I mean it’s just a drama you are playing
with yourself, you do not become primitive.

01:42:49.160 --> 01:42:54.891
This is the point is that and then the problem
is the brain is thinking the same way, that

01:42:54.891 --> 01:43:01.110
the same rate and everything the same, only
by changing is something that is not good

01:43:01.110 --> 01:43:02.810
because you should accept as you are.

01:43:02.810 --> 01:43:05.860
Why to do something like that?

01:43:05.860 --> 01:43:11.810
But simpler life means this way, that’s
another extreme.

01:43:11.810 --> 01:43:24.150
But you see too much of formality like having
a tail coat or wearing morning dress, grey

01:43:24.150 --> 01:43:29.220
suit and then having a particular type of
a glass for a thing and all that nonsense

01:43:29.220 --> 01:43:30.580
you see you better finish off.

01:43:30.580 --> 01:43:37.610
That’s bit too much going too far with it
and also caring for all these small, small

01:43:37.610 --> 01:43:43.490
things like matter that’s something that’s
grown in you.

01:43:43.490 --> 01:43:47.820
Preservation of horrible things and useless
things and all that it’s [really?].

01:43:47.820 --> 01:43:51.580
And then to think, think, think, think about
everything, sit down and think how miserable

01:43:51.580 --> 01:43:55.650
I am and when there is no misery you just
sit down and make miseries by thinking.

01:43:55.650 --> 01:43:59.060
I don’t find any thing miserable here, what
is there?

01:43:59.060 --> 01:44:04.430
You see in India these people where there
people are so happy, chirping just like birds

01:44:04.430 --> 01:44:05.430
enjoying themselves.

01:44:05.430 --> 01:44:09.160
They don’t have all the things that you
have.

01:44:09.160 --> 01:44:13.990
So you see to get out of materialism is a
better idea, to say that a simpler life means,

01:44:13.990 --> 01:44:15.790
but you must live beautifully.

01:44:15.790 --> 01:44:20.050
Beautiful doesn’t mean that you should have
ten types of things and all that.

01:44:20.050 --> 01:44:24.710
Beautifully means you should not be as a morbid
stinking, you see.

01:44:24.710 --> 01:44:32.150
Clean and beautiful you can make beauty out
of the soil anything; with love, you can do

01:44:32.150 --> 01:44:33.150
anything.

01:44:33.150 --> 01:44:36.970
So you see it’s alright I mean what ever
way you dress up or anything makes no difference

01:44:36.970 --> 01:44:38.760
that’s what I’m trying to say.

01:44:38.760 --> 01:44:41.400
That it is the inner thing that has to change
not the outer.

01:44:41.400 --> 01:44:43.230
Again the Sahaja Yoga is this.
